  <name>Bijiben</name>
  <summary>Quickly jot notes</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Notes is an editor allowing to make simple lists for later use.
    </p>
    <p>
      It allows to use ownCloud as a storage location and online editor.
    </p>
  </description>
